t: "That ňĻrewardňļ is the good news which God gives to His servants who believe and do good. Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúI do not ask you for a reward for this ňĻmessageňļ‚ÄĒonly honour for ňĻourňļ kinship.‚ÄĚ¬†Whoever earns a good deed, We will increase it in goodness for them. Surely God is All-Forgiving, Most Appreciative"